1
00:01:33,530 --> 00:01:35,030
[OVERDO]

2
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:37,850
[Episode 2]

3
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,000
Tonight is the engagement ceremony

4
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:50,150
for the 2 young masters
of the Murong family.

5
00:01:50,150 --> 00:01:52,560
This is a double blessing
for the Murong family.

6
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,280
I heard

7
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,539
Li Boze is also coming.

8
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:57,800
He's the child
the Murong family mistakenly took?

9
00:01:58,150 --> 00:02:00,150
He is the true son of both families.

10
00:02:00,370 --> 00:02:01,570
You're here too?

11
00:02:02,260 --> 00:02:03,600
Long time no see.

12
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:12,240
Qingyi.

13
00:02:12,560 --> 00:02:13,490
Long time no see.

14
00:02:14,080 --> 00:02:15,400
Father was worried about

15
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,260
your marriage in his last letter.

16
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:19,210
Worried about my marriage?

17
00:02:19,470 --> 00:02:20,590
I'm afraid what Li Rongzhang cares about

18
00:02:19,690 --> 00:02:22,020
[Li Boze, the only son of the Li family]

19
00:02:20,590 --> 00:02:21,750
is not my marriage.

20
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,960
He's afraid
the Huo family will leave him out

21
00:02:23,960 --> 00:02:26,160
and do business with the Murong family.

22
00:02:27,680 --> 00:02:28,280
Qingyi...

23
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:31,840
Dudu!

24
00:02:38,190 --> 00:02:38,870
Dudu.

25
00:02:40,000 --> 00:02:40,800
Sister.

26
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:43,680
Don't call me by my nickname
with so many people around.

27
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,590
Okay, Dudu.

28
00:02:45,590 --> 00:02:46,520
That jinx.

29
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:48,190
What nonsense did he spout this time?

30
00:02:48,190 --> 00:02:49,630
Just ignore him.

31
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:50,079
Come on.

32
00:02:50,079 --> 00:02:51,120
Sit with me.

33
00:02:51,310 --> 00:02:51,870
Sit.

34
00:02:55,520 --> 00:02:57,190
Sister, you've been learning English
recently?

35
00:02:57,190 --> 00:02:58,030
Yes.

36
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,590
They know Chinese.

37
00:03:03,960 --> 00:03:05,890
Sister, these flowers are for you.

38
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,030
I felt sorry
for the old lady selling flowers,

39
00:03:08,030 --> 00:03:08,960
so I bought some.

40
00:03:12,030 --> 00:03:12,840
How much?

41
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:13,590
Two silver dollars.

42
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:14,430
So expensive?

43
00:03:14,910 --> 00:03:16,040
You didn't bargain?

44
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,800
For you and Mother,

45
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:20,340
it's worth it no matter how much it costs.

46
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:23,190
Our Boze is so kind-hearted.

47
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:25,520
Unlike someone

48
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,310
who has no heart.

49
00:03:27,310 --> 00:03:27,870
No.

50
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,960
Someone with a rotten heart!

51
00:03:30,750 --> 00:03:31,560
Boze.

52
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:33,680
Mother.

53
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:37,630
You were just promoted to inspector

54
00:03:37,630 --> 00:03:38,520
and have been very busy,

55
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,380
yet you still made a special trip.

56
00:03:40,710 --> 00:03:41,570
This is for you.

57
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,520
On such a joyous day,

58
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:46,190
I must come and join the fun
no matter how busy I am.

59
00:03:46,190 --> 00:03:47,520
As long as you don't mind my being here.

60
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,470
How could I?

61
00:03:48,870 --> 00:03:49,590
However,

62
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,400
next time you give flowers to a girl,

63
00:03:52,470 --> 00:03:53,730
you should give roses.

64
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,030
Okay.

65
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,490
I'll remember that.

66
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,870
Madam Murong.

67
00:03:59,280 --> 00:04:00,410
Compared to Qingyi,

68
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:03,190
Boze looks more like your son.

69
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:08,590
He grew up by my side.

70
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:10,360
How could he be like
that ungrateful son of mine?

71
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,560
Come on, let's go in.

72
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:15,960
How is it?

73
00:04:16,269 --> 00:04:17,000
Have you been busy lately?

74
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,720
Not really.

75
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:21,120
Second Young Master.

76
00:04:21,120 --> 00:04:22,000
It's time to go.

77
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:28,000
Let's go.

78
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,600
Please welcome

79
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,870
Miss Huo Minxian.

80
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:51,430
Aren't you afraid I'll murder my husband?

81
00:04:52,190 --> 00:04:53,240
Miss Huo,

82
00:04:53,390 --> 00:04:55,720
if you really have such courage and means,

83
00:04:56,270 --> 00:04:58,070
I would actually appreciate it.

84
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,870
Just wait and see.

85
00:05:01,070 --> 00:05:02,750
Mr. Murong Qingyu, please

86
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:05,480
welcome your lifelong partner.

87
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,480
-So pretty.
-Yes.

88
00:05:16,370 --> 00:05:18,150
[Fang Mulan, the only daughter
of the Fang family in Nanyang]

89
00:05:32,310 --> 00:05:33,540
♪ The more passionate ♪

90
00:05:33,659 --> 00:05:35,750
♪ Our past embrace ♪

91
00:05:38,890 --> 00:05:40,140
♪ The more icy ♪

92
00:05:40,210 --> 00:05:42,430
♪ Our present clash ♪

93
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:46,430
♪ If not tangled in love ♪

94
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:49,970
♪ We are locked in hate ♪

95
00:05:51,090 --> 00:05:55,390
♪ There is no escaping it ♪

96
00:05:58,790 --> 00:06:00,220
♪ Sharper pain, deeper mark ♪

97
00:06:00,250 --> 00:06:02,300
♪ Deeper care, greater torment ♪

98
00:06:05,570 --> 00:06:06,790
♪ I won't give up on you ♪

99
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:09,010
♪ Don't let go of me ♪

100
00:06:11,430 --> 00:06:13,540
♪ Let the ropes of fate ♪

101
00:06:13,620 --> 00:06:16,420
♪ Bind you and me ♪

102
00:06:17,750 --> 00:06:19,950
♪ Even if led to a precipice ♪

103
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,690
♪ Together, we fall ♪

104
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:26,270
♪ Take away everything I have ♪

105
00:06:26,310 --> 00:06:28,150
♪ Can you bear the weight of it all? ♪

106
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:31,170
♪ I offer you my whole life ♪

107
00:06:31,290 --> 00:06:32,860
♪ In exchange for my everything ♪

108
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,810
♪ Will you finally be mine? ♪

109
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,810
♪ Give me love and hate ♪

110
00:06:37,950 --> 00:06:41,360
♪ Let the tears fall,
let the blood spill ♪

111
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:44,180
♪ Even through suffering,
I'll never let go of your hand ♪

112
00:06:45,060 --> 00:06:47,820
♪ I can't break free, I can't escape ♪

113
00:06:47,850 --> 00:06:50,330
♪ This, too, can be called
a lifetime together ♪

114
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:50,480
This is the only daughter
of the Fang family in Nanyang,

115
00:06:50,409 --> 00:06:51,610
♪ We ♪

116
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,360
Fang Mulan.

117
00:06:53,060 --> 00:06:54,659
♪ Remain bound by fate until the end ♪

118
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:55,120
You should call her sister-in-law.

119
00:06:55,990 --> 00:07:00,110
♪ Forevermore ♪

120
00:07:12,580 --> 00:07:14,680
♪ Neither you nor I ♪

121
00:07:16,390 --> 00:07:17,430
Sister-in-law.

122
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:19,200
♪ Can ever break free ♪

123
00:07:57,470 --> 00:08:00,080
[Beicheng Mailbox]

124
00:08:00,620 --> 00:08:03,360
[Three Years Ago]

125
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:07,850
[Beicheng]

126
00:08:07,560 --> 00:08:09,480
This house has been empty for years

127
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,010
since the last tenant left.

128
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,660
Please come in.

129
00:08:23,950 --> 00:08:24,920
Old Zhang said

130
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:26,600
it was a young master who studied abroad

131
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:27,310
and just returned

132
00:08:27,310 --> 00:08:28,640
looking to rent a house.

133
00:08:29,240 --> 00:08:30,160
I didn't believe it.

134
00:08:30,160 --> 00:08:32,600
Why would a rich person
rent this kind of house?

135
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,659
Until he mentioned

136
00:08:33,669 --> 00:08:34,440
that the newly opened clinic

137
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,169
west of the footbridge is yours

138
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,510
and that you wanted to find a place

139
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,120
close to the clinic.

140
00:08:39,510 --> 00:08:40,240
So it turns out

141
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:42,909
the living Buddha
who treats the poor lately

142
00:08:42,909 --> 00:08:43,630
is you.

143
00:08:44,390 --> 00:08:45,480
I am no Buddha.

144
00:08:46,150 --> 00:08:48,010
I charge for my medical services.

145
00:08:48,150 --> 00:08:49,360
You're still a good person.

146
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:51,240
I must help you find a house
to your liking.

147
00:08:51,240 --> 00:08:51,840
Am I right?

148
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,510
What do you think?

149
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:56,870
Well...

150
00:08:58,550 --> 00:08:59,200
How about

151
00:08:59,360 --> 00:09:00,890
I show you a few more places?

152
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:03,360
You look like a young master
from a wealthy family.

153
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:06,120
I'm afraid you won't get used to
living in a small house like this,

154
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,720
and your family would worry.

155
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,270
My family?

156
00:09:16,200 --> 00:09:17,400
I don't have a family.

157
00:09:18,320 --> 00:09:19,450
And I don't need one.

158
00:09:26,960 --> 00:09:27,630
Bastard!

159
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,870
I knew he wasn't mine.

160
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:31,600
Tell him to get out.

161
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,200
Go back to the Murong family!

162
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,670
The one who was properly settled

163
00:09:37,670 --> 00:09:38,800
was the other child.

164
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,550
If it weren't for you,

165
00:09:41,550 --> 00:09:42,840
how could your father have died?

166
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,910
You jinx!

167
00:09:44,030 --> 00:09:44,870
Ever since you came back,

168
00:09:44,870 --> 00:09:46,200
our family has suffered terrible luck!

169
00:09:46,200 --> 00:09:48,960
But I became a burden, passed
back and forth between the two families,

170
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,120
barely scraping by.

171
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:01,080
Both the husband and wife
got tuberculosis,

172
00:10:01,080 --> 00:10:02,340
and they are dirt poor.

173
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,780
What do you think they will do?

174
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:07,460
What's there to guess?

175
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,320
In the face of life and death,

176
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:11,920
of course
they'll only care about themselves.

177
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,420
What are you doing?

178
00:10:27,630 --> 00:10:28,840
You don't read these letters anyway!

179
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:29,440
Exactly!

180
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,150
Cheapskate!

181
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:30,720
Go.

182
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,320
Leave!

183
00:10:31,480 --> 00:10:32,110
-Go home.
-What a cheapskate!

184
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,960
Cheapskate! Cheapskate!

185
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:51,000
[Jiujiekou Street, East District,
Beicheng]

186
00:10:50,240 --> 00:10:51,120
These letters

187
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,930
[To Lan, No. 27 Liuli Alley]

188
00:10:51,790 --> 00:10:53,390
were all sent from Nancheng.

189
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,870
But they weren't for me.

190
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:58,390
Don't think that by hiding,

191
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,600
I can't deal with you.

192
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,550
You're probably cowering
in some gutter drinking dirty water.

193
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:03,750
You must have stolen my money

194
00:11:03,750 --> 00:11:05,840
and been too guilty to show your face,
right?

195
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:07,120
Now that things have turned out like this,

196
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,980
it's all your fault, you bastard.

197
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,150
Cutting off your hands

198
00:11:10,150 --> 00:11:11,200
and peeling your skin

199
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,150
wouldn't be enough to quell my anger!

200
00:11:13,150 --> 00:11:14,440
I hope you get what you deserve.

201
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:17,970
You'd better smash your head
against the wall of the orphanage.

202
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,380
Cursing so viciously.

203
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,640
What kind of deep hatred is this?

204
00:11:30,910 --> 00:11:31,510
Wait.

205
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,370
Something's wrong.

206
00:11:56,720 --> 00:11:57,960
I see.

207
00:12:01,050 --> 00:12:02,220
[It's all your fault.
Cutting off your hands...]

208
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,030
The person

209
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:33,090
you're looking for is not here.

210
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:35,630
Before I moved in,

211
00:12:35,870 --> 00:12:37,930
this house had been vacant for years.

212
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:40,150
If you are really worried about him,

213
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:41,480
you can call the police.

214
00:12:49,950 --> 00:12:51,920
[R]

215
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,880
Come on, two more people.

216
00:12:58,510 --> 00:13:03,820
[Nancheng]

217
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:18,020
[Ren Susu]

218
00:13:15,720 --> 00:13:16,510
It's done.

219
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:21,480
How do you like it?

220
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:25,390
It's so beautiful.

221
00:13:25,510 --> 00:13:26,390
I like it.

222
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,150
Thank you.

223
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:31,790
Thanks.

224
00:13:32,360 --> 00:13:34,910
The ship arrived before you
came from Beicheng, right?

225
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:35,600
Yes.

226
00:13:37,870 --> 00:13:39,470
Then have you seen this girl?

227
00:13:39,510 --> 00:13:40,550
She has a mole on her left cheek.

228
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:41,950
She's easy to recognize.

229
00:13:45,240 --> 00:13:46,370
I've never seen her.

230
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,750
Miss Ren, you're back?

231
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:04,630
We made scallion oil noodles.

232
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:05,560
Do you want some?

233
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:07,630
Thank you, Landlady.

234
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,290
But I've already eaten.

235
00:14:14,390 --> 00:14:15,910
This delicate-looking girl

236
00:14:15,910 --> 00:14:17,080
is well-educated.

237
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:19,080
Why does she have to make a living

238
00:14:19,320 --> 00:14:20,520
at the dock every day?

239
00:14:20,720 --> 00:14:22,720
The dock is busy with people
coming and going,

240
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:24,200
and news travels fast there.

241
00:14:24,200 --> 00:14:26,600
She seems to be looking for her sister.

242
00:14:26,870 --> 00:14:29,030
She looks frail and is always

243
00:14:29,030 --> 00:14:29,960
a loner.

244
00:14:31,200 --> 00:14:34,600
She has traveled across half of China
looking for her sister.

245
00:14:49,240 --> 00:14:49,910
The person

246
00:14:50,240 --> 00:14:51,970
you're looking for is not here.

247
00:14:52,960 --> 00:14:54,480
Before I moved in,

248
00:14:54,750 --> 00:14:56,810
this house had been vacant for years.

249
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,030
If you are really worried about him,

250
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,360
you can call the police.

251
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:04,240
Who are you?

252
00:15:04,910 --> 00:15:05,910
Why did you say I'm worried about him

253
00:15:05,910 --> 00:15:07,040
and looking for him?

254
00:15:07,270 --> 00:15:08,270
Do you know him?

255
00:15:08,750 --> 00:15:10,270
A true heart

256
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:12,130
cannot be completely concealed.

257
00:15:13,200 --> 00:15:14,390
If you hate someone,

258
00:15:14,790 --> 00:15:17,030
you wouldn't,
without getting any response,

259
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:19,080
send dozens of abusive letters.

260
00:15:21,120 --> 00:15:21,910
Besides,

261
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:24,510
the language in your letters
is extremely dirty.

262
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:26,710
It seems like you're collecting a debt.

263
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:27,630
In fact,

264
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,360
you're being vague,

265
00:15:29,840 --> 00:15:32,440
and you deliberately mentioned
an orphanage.

266
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:36,000
Our agreement remains.

267
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,030
Looking forward to your reply.

268
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:39,670
[Our] [agreement] [remains.]
[Looking] [forward] [to] [your] [reply.]

269
00:15:38,480 --> 00:15:40,680
Did you really think I wouldn't notice?

270
00:15:41,990 --> 00:15:45,320
[Our] [agreement] [remains.]
[Looking] [forward] [to] [your] [reply.]

271
00:15:49,670 --> 00:15:50,480
You must have

272
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:52,670
sent this letter to many addresses,

273
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:55,800
but it was always like a stone
dropped into the sea.

274
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:56,870
If you had an agreement,

275
00:15:56,870 --> 00:15:57,790
and he broke it,

276
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,440
you should stop looking.

277
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,790
Either he's dead,

278
00:16:01,270 --> 00:16:02,000
or...

279
00:16:02,270 --> 00:16:04,200
he just can't be bothered to reply.

280
00:16:05,750 --> 00:16:07,410
People are born to walk alone.

281
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:08,750
Don't waste your energy

282
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:09,720
on others.

283
00:16:15,030 --> 00:16:16,480
You're talking nonsense!

284
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:17,670
Lan is not dead!

285
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,560
Take back your curse!

286
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,750
Did I...

287
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,270
make you cry?

288
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:46,000
I knew this letter

289
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,260
would likely never reach her.

290
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:51,600
You're smart.

291
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,920
You spot the hidden message.

292
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,520
But you're also vicious.

293
00:16:58,200 --> 00:17:00,030
You could have chosen to ignore it,

294
00:17:00,030 --> 00:17:01,440
yet you mocked our agreement

295
00:17:01,440 --> 00:17:02,480
and her life.

296
00:17:04,960 --> 00:17:07,490
Does guessing a stranger's life
and feelings

297
00:17:07,640 --> 00:17:09,440
give you a sense of superiority?

298
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:14,349
"People are born to walk alone."

299
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:17,200
That's because you haven't met someone
who stands by you

300
00:17:17,200 --> 00:17:20,000
through thick and thin
and would never forget you.

301
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:22,079
That is your misfortune.

302
00:17:24,880 --> 00:17:26,010
So I don't blame you.

303
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:34,880
My misfortune?

304
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:36,750
Ridiculous.

305
00:17:58,590 --> 00:18:00,030
Don't worry, Lan.

306
00:18:00,720 --> 00:18:02,250
I'll soon save enough money

307
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,490
to find you in Beicheng.

308
00:18:08,130 --> 00:18:10,280
[Xinyi Clinic]

309
00:18:09,510 --> 00:18:10,240
Doctor,

310
00:18:10,400 --> 00:18:12,030
this is all I have.

311
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:28,510
Both the husband and wife
got tuberculosis,

312
00:18:28,510 --> 00:18:29,770
and they are dirt poor.

313
00:18:30,550 --> 00:18:32,150
What do you think they'll do?

314
00:18:33,590 --> 00:18:34,850
What's there to guess?

315
00:18:35,590 --> 00:18:36,720
In the face of life and death,

316
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:39,320
of course
they'll only care about themselves.

317
00:18:41,960 --> 00:18:42,510
Okay.

318
00:18:42,590 --> 00:18:44,000
Go to the nurse for your IV.

319
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:45,510
Please save my husband.

320
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:48,280
Don't tell him I was here.

321
00:18:48,510 --> 00:18:50,400
Just say the money for the treatment

322
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,400
came from you,

323
00:18:51,400 --> 00:18:52,110
okay?

324
00:18:59,830 --> 00:19:01,240
The wife sold her dowry.

325
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:02,290
[Land and Property Ownership Certificate]

326
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:02,590
Look at this.

327
00:19:08,100 --> 00:19:09,590
[Land and Property Ownership Certificate]

328
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,680
The husband wants to mortgage the house

329
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,920
to treat his wife,

330
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:12,960
and he also begged us not to let her know.

331
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:14,090
What about himself?

332
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,880
He said he was giving up treatment

333
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:18,810
and going out to work to earn money.

334
00:19:19,310 --> 00:19:20,040
He just left.

335
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,880
Honey, come back!

336
00:19:24,720 --> 00:19:25,400
Excuse me!

337
00:19:25,400 --> 00:19:27,160
Why did you sell the house?

338
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,000
Why?

339
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,240
What about you?

340
00:19:29,240 --> 00:19:30,680
Why?

341
00:19:31,270 --> 00:19:32,270
Say something!

342
00:19:32,270 --> 00:19:33,680
Why?

343
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,570
I can give up everything

344
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:37,180
just to keep you alive.

345
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:43,270
-Someone who stands by you through thick and thin
-Someone who stands by you through thick and thin

346
00:19:43,270 --> 00:19:46,470
-and would never forget you.
-and would never forget you.

347
00:20:00,790 --> 00:20:02,110
Lan is not dead!

348
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:03,440
Take back your curse!

349
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:04,000
[Lan is not dead! Take back your curse!]

350
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:05,000
[We barely know each other. Why are you
being such a downer all of a sudden?]

351
00:20:05,000 --> 00:20:06,690
[Don't respond to me like this anymore.]

352
00:20:16,310 --> 00:20:17,680
Miss Crybaby,

353
00:20:18,400 --> 00:20:20,200
hope this letter finds you well.

354
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:21,550
I'm sorry.

355
00:20:21,830 --> 00:20:22,880
As a doctor,

356
00:20:23,270 --> 00:20:26,070
I've seen all the darkness of human nature
in the face of life and death.

357
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:28,130
I deliberately said some mean things

358
00:20:28,440 --> 00:20:30,030
to pass my bad mood onto you.

359
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:33,000
Dragging others into a miserable mood

360
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:35,550
similar to mine in just a few words

361
00:20:35,830 --> 00:20:37,350
and taking pleasure in it

362
00:20:37,880 --> 00:20:39,110
is what I'm good at.

363
00:20:41,680 --> 00:20:42,940
I still firmly believe

364
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:45,330
that people are born to walk alone.

365
00:20:46,110 --> 00:20:47,510
But along the journey,

366
00:20:48,350 --> 00:20:50,510
there might occasionally
be fellow travelers.

367
00:20:50,510 --> 00:20:52,400
So I believe your Lan

368
00:20:53,110 --> 00:20:54,970
will show up for the appointment.

369
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:10,680
P.S.,

370
00:21:11,440 --> 00:21:13,900
there are many ways
to hide secret messages.

371
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:16,220
Why did it have to be an insulting letter?

372
00:21:45,550 --> 00:21:46,510
Mr. Duhuo,

373
00:21:47,000 --> 00:21:48,800
hope this letter finds you well.

374
00:21:51,160 --> 00:21:52,790
Duhuo?

375
00:21:55,590 --> 00:21:57,160
Mr. Duhuo?

376
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:01,750
If others see an insulting letter,

377
00:22:01,750 --> 00:22:03,750
they would throw it away like trash.

378
00:22:03,750 --> 00:22:05,750
But if she sees an insulting letter,

379
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:07,790
she'll know it's a greeting from me.

380
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,200
In hell,

381
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:10,110
curses and pain

382
00:22:10,310 --> 00:22:13,040
are proof
that we endured the darkness together.

383
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:14,480
It's hard to explain to you,

384
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:16,110
but I accept your apology.

385
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:18,730
And I'm a bit curious about you.

386
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:20,310
You see yourself as a cold person,

387
00:22:20,310 --> 00:22:22,070
but your career choice as a doctor

388
00:22:22,070 --> 00:22:23,730
already shows your kindness.

389
00:22:24,750 --> 00:22:25,160
P.S.,

390
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:28,440
a doctor who believes
people are born to walk alone

391
00:22:28,440 --> 00:22:31,170
is perfectly suited to the name
of the herb Duhuo.

392
00:22:31,550 --> 00:22:32,150
P.P.S.,

393
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:33,830
I'm not a crybaby.

394
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:34,860
I am very brave.

395
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:36,440
P.P.P.S.,

396
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:37,790
I'm a boy.

397
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:41,640
A boy?

398
00:22:45,480 --> 00:22:46,550
Mr. Duhuo?

399
00:22:52,720 --> 00:22:54,200
Mr. Brave Crybaby,

400
00:22:54,350 --> 00:22:55,440
hope this letter finds you well.

401
00:22:55,440 --> 00:22:58,040
Your neat handwriting
and scented stationery

402
00:22:58,110 --> 00:22:59,960
really scream masculinity.

403
00:23:00,880 --> 00:23:01,960
I assume you

404
00:23:01,960 --> 00:23:05,090
must be an elegant gentleman
with extraordinary grace.

405
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:06,200
As for me,

406
00:23:06,350 --> 00:23:07,400
I'm 5 chi tall,

407
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,310
dark as the bottom of a pot,

408
00:23:08,310 --> 00:23:09,720
with a strange temper

409
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:11,290
and a biting tongue.

410
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:13,750
I'm really not worth being curious about.

411
00:23:13,750 --> 00:23:15,610
The name you gave me is quite good.

412
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:17,030
Duhuo treats gout.

413
00:23:17,350 --> 00:23:18,480
I treat madness.

414
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:20,070
If you need it,

415
00:23:20,070 --> 00:23:21,110
I'll give you
a 10% discount on the consultation fee.

416
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:21,720
P.S.,

417
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,640
even someone as mean as me

418
00:23:23,830 --> 00:23:25,270
can't understand why two people

419
00:23:25,270 --> 00:23:27,310
would treat insults as greetings.

420
00:23:29,860 --> 00:23:33,390
[Xinyi Clinic]

421
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:35,270
Mr. Duhuo,

422
00:23:35,880 --> 00:23:37,510
at my art school,

423
00:23:37,790 --> 00:23:39,390
my classmates all praise me,

424
00:23:39,510 --> 00:23:41,510
saying I have a prominent Adam's apple,

425
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:43,720
broad shoulders
that could carry the world,

426
00:23:43,720 --> 00:23:45,720
and the strength to move mountains—

427
00:23:45,880 --> 00:23:48,140
a truly unmatched strong man of our time.

428
00:23:48,440 --> 00:23:49,590
I casually drew a little sketch

429
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:50,680
for you to imagine

430
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,580
my fit and handsome demeanor.

431
00:23:54,770 --> 00:23:58,190
[Me]

432
00:24:01,630 --> 00:24:02,990
[You]

433
00:24:04,080 --> 00:24:05,020
[You]

434
00:24:05,440 --> 00:24:06,320
[Me]

435
00:24:06,380 --> 00:24:07,160
[You]

436
00:24:10,730 --> 00:24:11,150
[Outline of Acupuncture Medicine]

437
00:24:11,340 --> 00:24:12,550
[Comprehensive Human Anatomy]

438
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:20,410
Scientifically speaking,

439
00:24:20,510 --> 00:24:22,640
those two "male traits" you mentioned

440
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:23,830
aren't necessary indicators

441
00:24:23,830 --> 00:24:25,590
of a strong physique.

442
00:24:26,160 --> 00:24:27,790
I'm attaching an anatomical sketch
of the human body

443
00:24:27,790 --> 00:24:29,320
to set the record straight.

444
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,310
What a pervert!

445
00:24:35,310 --> 00:24:36,480
Pervert?

446
00:24:39,070 --> 00:24:42,330
Please don't slander
the human physiological structure.

447
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:44,960
In a doctor's eyes,
it's nothing more than bones, muscles,

448
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:46,490
blood vessels, and nerves.

449
00:24:46,510 --> 00:24:47,310
That's all.

450
00:24:47,550 --> 00:24:48,750
If I scared you,

451
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:52,270
I'm attaching the autumn scenery
of Beicheng to this letter

452
00:24:52,270 --> 00:24:53,670
to express my apologies.

453
00:24:59,270 --> 00:25:00,960
In Beicheng, it is already autumn,
and the leaves have started to fall.

454
00:25:00,960 --> 00:25:03,590
The parasol trees in Nancheng
are still lush and green.

455
00:25:03,590 --> 00:25:04,960
Even if I jumped as high
as I possibly could,

456
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:06,720
I still wouldn't reach a single leaf.

457
00:25:06,720 --> 00:25:07,920
So I can only send

458
00:25:08,160 --> 00:25:10,420
some palmiers in summer with the letter.

459
00:25:25,590 --> 00:25:26,720
Meng, is it good?

460
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:27,720
Yes, it is.

461
00:25:28,110 --> 00:25:28,640
You can have these all.

462
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:30,240
I'll buy you some more later.

463
00:25:32,960 --> 00:25:33,790
Try some too.

464
00:25:49,000 --> 00:25:50,550
The weather is getting cold,

465
00:25:50,550 --> 00:25:52,080
and winter is approaching.

466
00:25:52,750 --> 00:25:54,640
I miss my mother's braised pork.

467
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,120
That's the taste of home.

468
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,110
Mom,

469
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:01,440
have some braised pork.

470
00:26:02,200 --> 00:26:03,880
Mom, is it good?

471
00:26:04,200 --> 00:26:05,160
Yes.

472
00:26:06,070 --> 00:26:07,110
I once...

473
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:10,400
perhaps had people I could call family.

474
00:26:13,920 --> 00:26:18,590
Moonlight shines on the ground.

475
00:26:19,350 --> 00:26:23,640
Little baby, go to sleep.

476
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:29,110
Moonlight shines on the ground...

477
00:26:29,310 --> 00:26:30,570
You are a born bad seed!

478
00:26:30,750 --> 00:26:32,010
Do you even deserve it?

479
00:26:32,030 --> 00:26:32,640
Trash!

480
00:26:32,750 --> 00:26:34,110
Hopeless!

481
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:36,310
You think you deserve to be a member
of the Murong family?

482
00:26:36,310 --> 00:26:37,830
Why don't you just die?

483
00:26:38,440 --> 00:26:40,040
But I still don't understand

484
00:26:40,510 --> 00:26:41,910
what the taste of home is.

485
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,930
According to your letters,

486
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:47,280
you seem to have had a rough life.

487
00:26:47,720 --> 00:26:49,250
Then why are you so attached

488
00:26:49,790 --> 00:26:50,960
to your home?

489
00:26:52,400 --> 00:26:53,600
I went home recently,

490
00:26:53,960 --> 00:26:55,880
and Mom
kept saying I've lost weight again.

491
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,720
She cooked a table full of good food.

492
00:26:57,720 --> 00:26:59,790
Dad fixed the swing in the yard.

493
00:27:00,590 --> 00:27:01,200
In this warm autumn,

494
00:27:01,200 --> 00:27:03,200
the garden is full of blooming flowers.

495
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,030
I think...

496
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:06,440
maybe this is the taste of home.

497
00:27:32,030 --> 00:27:32,750
Qingyi.

498
00:27:34,030 --> 00:27:34,890
Is this Qingyi?

499
00:27:36,030 --> 00:27:36,960
Yes.

500
00:27:37,350 --> 00:27:38,280
It really is you!

501
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:41,030
Qingyi,

502
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:43,750
why did you return from abroad
without saying a word?

503
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:45,310
Do you know
how long I've been looking for you?

504
00:27:45,310 --> 00:27:46,310
Where are you now?

505
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,200
Qingyu.

506
00:27:55,830 --> 00:27:57,430
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival.

507
00:28:07,790 --> 00:28:09,390
Happy Mid-Autumn Festival.

508
00:28:10,480 --> 00:28:11,200
Qingyi.

509
00:28:12,000 --> 00:28:13,200
I guess you're living

510
00:28:14,030 --> 00:28:15,230
a very happy life now,

511
00:28:15,720 --> 00:28:16,480
aren't you?

512
00:28:19,640 --> 00:28:20,310
Qingyu,

513
00:28:21,200 --> 00:28:21,880
I...

514
00:28:22,400 --> 00:28:23,750
met a girl.

515
00:28:24,830 --> 00:28:26,030
She's quite strange.

516
00:28:26,960 --> 00:28:27,480
No.

517
00:28:27,960 --> 00:28:28,920
It should be...

518
00:28:29,350 --> 00:28:30,810
she's quite interesting.

519
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:36,000
Thinking of home,

520
00:28:36,400 --> 00:28:38,830
I usually only feel anger and resentment.

521
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:41,480
But hearing you talk about home,

522
00:28:41,920 --> 00:28:43,070
I inexplicably

523
00:28:43,830 --> 00:28:44,830
called my only family member

524
00:28:44,830 --> 00:28:46,690
during the Mid-Autumn Festival.

525
00:28:47,510 --> 00:28:49,200
Hearing that he was doing well,

526
00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:50,330
I was very relieved.

527
00:28:52,790 --> 00:28:54,240
Please make me look good.

528
00:28:54,880 --> 00:28:56,740
Are you sending it to your family?

529
00:28:57,400 --> 00:28:58,070
Not family.

530
00:28:58,070 --> 00:28:58,720
It's...

531
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:01,320
Your sweetheart, right?

532
00:29:02,510 --> 00:29:03,350
Here we go.

533
00:29:04,750 --> 00:29:05,480
Smile.

534
00:29:05,640 --> 00:29:06,200
Okay.

535
00:29:06,510 --> 00:29:06,920
Ready.

536
00:29:06,920 --> 00:29:07,640
Three,

537
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:09,480
two,

538
00:29:09,830 --> 00:29:10,400
one!

539
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:15,550
There's a gift enclosed with this letter.

540
00:29:15,550 --> 00:29:16,270
Thank you.

541
00:29:17,440 --> 00:29:18,550
If it weren't for you,

542
00:29:18,550 --> 00:29:20,610
I wouldn't have contacted my family.

543
00:29:20,640 --> 00:29:22,370
Looking forward to your reply.

544
00:29:45,790 --> 00:29:48,000
You haven't written back in over a month.

545
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:48,880
Have you been

546
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:50,890
busy with your studies recently?

547
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,790
As soon as winter started,

548
00:29:56,790 --> 00:29:58,880
the clinic got crowded with patients.

549
00:29:58,880 --> 00:30:01,610
I asked my brother to find your place
in Nancheng.

550
00:30:01,920 --> 00:30:03,720
The landlord said you moved out.

551
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:09,700
The winter here
is getting colder every day.

552
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:12,160
Before spring comes,

553
00:30:12,160 --> 00:30:13,960
will I receive a letter from you?

554
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:21,160
Why are you ignoring me?

555
00:30:47,110 --> 00:30:48,570
Please enjoy yourselves.

556
00:30:51,480 --> 00:30:53,740
-Congratulations.
-Congratulations.

557
00:30:54,110 --> 00:30:55,160
Miss Fang and Young Master Qingyu,

558
00:30:55,160 --> 00:30:56,830
you are a match made in heaven.

559
00:30:57,160 --> 00:30:57,830
Thank you.

560
00:30:58,160 --> 00:30:59,000
Now that you're engaged,

561
00:30:59,000 --> 00:31:00,830
when is the wedding?

562
00:31:02,000 --> 00:31:02,750
It'll be soon.

563
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:04,240
Ren Susu?

564
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:07,270
You're not dead?

565
00:31:14,240 --> 00:31:15,300
Congratulations.

566
00:31:15,510 --> 00:31:16,840
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

567
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,290
Where have you been?

568
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:21,000
Everyone is waiting for us to toast.

569
00:31:21,790 --> 00:31:23,590
You insisted on this engagement.

570
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:25,250
Can you at least act properly?

571
00:31:26,680 --> 00:31:28,640
Who said I insisted on it?

572
00:31:58,480 --> 00:32:00,410
You shouldn't leave Miss Huo alone

573
00:32:00,440 --> 00:32:01,840
to entertain the guests.

574
00:32:03,480 --> 00:32:05,410
Since you agreed to this marriage,

575
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:07,110
you should be a gentleman.

576
00:32:08,200 --> 00:32:09,640
It's just putting up with being cheated on

577
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:11,440
in exchange for some resources.

578
00:32:12,510 --> 00:32:14,910
Yet they had to hold
an engagement ceremony

579
00:32:15,160 --> 00:32:17,440
to cover up their naked ambitions.

580
00:32:19,550 --> 00:32:20,440
Don't let

581
00:32:20,920 --> 00:32:22,200
Mother hear that.

582
00:32:22,200 --> 00:32:23,400
Don't worry, Qingyu.

583
00:32:23,590 --> 00:32:25,510
I won't fight you for the throne.

584
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:26,680
After all,

585
00:32:26,920 --> 00:32:28,030
if you get upset,

586
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,310
you might send me to prison again

587
00:32:29,310 --> 00:32:30,840
for another several years.

588
00:32:31,200 --> 00:32:32,400
I can't afford that.

589
00:32:33,510 --> 00:32:34,160
Qingyi.

590
00:32:34,830 --> 00:32:35,680
What happened 3 years ago

591
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:36,750
wasn't what you thought.

592
00:32:36,750 --> 00:32:37,830
How?

593
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:39,800
Don't you agree with them

594
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:41,480
that I killed Huo Mingxi?

595
00:32:41,480 --> 00:32:43,480
Do you really think I believed that?

596
00:32:55,510 --> 00:32:56,270
Forget it.

597
00:32:57,590 --> 00:32:59,120
Let's focus on the present.

598
00:33:04,830 --> 00:33:06,160
You still have the right

599
00:33:06,240 --> 00:33:07,960
to call off this wedding.

600
00:33:09,030 --> 00:33:10,830
Here is a boat ticket to England.

601
00:33:12,270 --> 00:33:13,530
You can leave anytime.

602
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,790
I'll handle the rest.

603
00:33:16,480 --> 00:33:18,110
You can continue studying medicine

604
00:33:18,110 --> 00:33:19,510
and do what you want to do.

605
00:33:28,310 --> 00:33:29,030
Qingyi.

606
00:33:30,640 --> 00:33:31,510
I don't want you to spend the rest

607
00:33:31,510 --> 00:33:33,170
of your life living in hatred.

608
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:35,290
You are still young.

609
00:33:35,920 --> 00:33:36,980
As long as you want,

610
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:38,310
you can still become

611
00:33:38,310 --> 00:33:39,750
the best surgeon.

612
00:33:40,960 --> 00:33:42,360
I will fully support you.

613
00:33:47,680 --> 00:33:49,480
Instead of planning for me,

614
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:52,220
you should care more about your fiancée.

615
00:33:53,350 --> 00:33:54,790
She is 100 times

616
00:33:55,070 --> 00:33:56,800
more dangerous than you think.

617
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:05,590
You only met her today.

618
00:34:05,720 --> 00:34:06,780
Why do you say that?

619
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:09,969
How did you meet her?

620
00:34:10,710 --> 00:34:12,920
Her father
is a wealthy merchant in Nanyang.

621
00:34:12,920 --> 00:34:14,630
When I went to Nanyang a year ago,

622
00:34:14,630 --> 00:34:15,960
he held me in high regard

623
00:34:16,760 --> 00:34:18,760
and wanted to form a marriage alliance
with the Murong family

624
00:34:18,760 --> 00:34:22,000
to secure the Fang family's
future influence in Nancheng.

625
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:23,860
After discussing it with Mother,

626
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,739
we felt that this marriage

627
00:34:25,800 --> 00:34:27,929
would be beneficial to both families.

628
00:34:30,630 --> 00:34:32,510
Here we go again.

629
00:34:34,360 --> 00:34:35,560
What about yourself?

630
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:37,070
Do you like her?

631
00:34:42,000 --> 00:34:42,710
Qingyi.

632
00:34:44,150 --> 00:34:45,000
In this world,

633
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:47,940
not everything
can be based on what you like.

634
00:34:48,550 --> 00:34:49,880
Marriages between prominent families

635
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:51,760
are about interests, not feelings.

636
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,889
As the eldest son of the Murong family,

637
00:34:54,190 --> 00:34:55,280
such a marriage

638
00:34:55,920 --> 00:34:57,180
is my responsibility.

639
00:35:08,550 --> 00:35:09,480
Moreover,

640
00:35:10,670 --> 00:35:12,400
she is a sensible and good girl.

641
00:35:15,440 --> 00:35:16,590
A good girl?

642
00:35:17,480 --> 00:35:18,610
Do you know her well?

643
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:20,220
She is smart and sensible.

644
00:35:20,590 --> 00:35:21,800
We exchanged letters

645
00:35:21,960 --> 00:35:23,000
and talked about everything.

646
00:35:23,000 --> 00:35:24,130
Exchanged letters?

647
00:35:32,470 --> 00:35:32,930
[To Lan]

648
00:35:33,630 --> 00:35:34,510
[Jiujiekou Street, East District,
Beicheng]

649
00:35:34,530 --> 00:35:35,290
[To Lan, No. 27 Liuli Alley]

650
00:35:38,640 --> 00:35:39,320
[Crybaby]

651
00:35:49,560 --> 00:35:50,020
[You]

652
00:35:51,670 --> 00:35:52,320
Qingyi.

653
00:35:55,070 --> 00:35:56,360
Do you really think you know her?

654
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:57,490
Haven't you thought

655
00:35:58,280 --> 00:35:59,210
that maybe she is

656
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:01,280
not what you think she is at all?

657
00:36:02,800 --> 00:36:03,510
Qingyu,

658
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:05,000
do you know

659
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,530
that Miss Fang is...

660
00:36:07,630 --> 00:36:08,670
Why are you here?

661
00:36:09,550 --> 00:36:10,230
Qingyu,

662
00:36:10,480 --> 00:36:11,680
I was looking for you.

663
00:36:13,150 --> 00:36:15,550
Did someone outside
want to have a drink with you?

664
00:36:15,550 --> 00:36:16,440
Not at all.

665
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:18,070
Just in time.

666
00:36:18,070 --> 00:36:19,470
Qingyi, you're here too.

667
00:36:19,880 --> 00:36:20,670
This matter

668
00:36:20,670 --> 00:36:21,930
is also related to you.

669
00:36:35,510 --> 00:36:37,320
The projectionist was knocked unconscious.

670
00:36:37,320 --> 00:36:39,050
Only this was left at the scene.

671
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,190
So it was you?

672
00:37:04,070 --> 00:37:05,190
I've heard about

673
00:37:05,320 --> 00:37:06,800
the Huo family's situation
for a long time.

674
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:08,360
I also heard that

675
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:10,360
Miss Huo's negatives had been lost.

676
00:37:10,360 --> 00:37:12,000
I had my family investigate

677
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:13,410
and bought them.

678
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:14,920
Mulan,

679
00:37:15,400 --> 00:37:17,000
thank you for your hard work.

680
00:37:17,630 --> 00:37:18,890
It's a trivial matter,

681
00:37:19,110 --> 00:37:20,370
not worth mentioning.

682
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:22,360
It's just that if this box of negatives

683
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:24,230
had fallen into the wrong hands,

684
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:28,320
it wouldn't be good
for Miss Huo or the Murong family,

685
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,450
especially for you,

686
00:37:29,510 --> 00:37:30,230
Qingyi.

687
00:37:30,550 --> 00:37:32,080
But you don't need to worry.

688
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:34,650
No matter who wants this box of negatives,

689
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:35,440
our Fang family

690
00:37:35,440 --> 00:37:37,970
can stop them
before they even get the chance.

691
00:37:39,320 --> 00:37:40,800
Take this box of negatives

692
00:37:41,150 --> 00:37:43,030
as a meeting gift from me,

693
00:37:43,230 --> 00:37:44,760
your sister-in-law.

694
00:37:52,320 --> 00:37:53,760
Striking first

695
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:55,010
and threatening me?

696
00:37:55,360 --> 00:37:56,590
I'd like to see

697
00:37:57,000 --> 00:37:58,590
what exactly you're up to.

698
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:01,090
♪ Sharper pain, deeper mark ♪

699
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:03,200
♪ Deeper care, greater torment ♪

700
00:38:05,960 --> 00:38:07,440
Qingyu, you are upright and noble.

701
00:38:06,270 --> 00:38:07,630
♪ I won't give up on you ♪

702
00:38:07,660 --> 00:38:09,930
♪ Don't let go of me ♪

703
00:38:07,710 --> 00:38:10,030
And Sister-in-law, you are understanding
and considerate.

704
00:38:10,030 --> 00:38:11,400
You are a perfect match

705
00:38:11,400 --> 00:38:12,670
made in heaven.

706
00:38:12,270 --> 00:38:14,380
♪ Let the ropes of fate ♪

707
00:38:13,230 --> 00:38:14,110
Unlike me,

708
00:38:14,460 --> 00:38:17,190
♪ Bind you and me ♪

709
00:38:14,510 --> 00:38:16,170
who crawled out of the gutter.

710
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:18,880
A domineering and vicious woman
like Huo Minxian

711
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:20,880
♪ Even if led to a precipice ♪

712
00:38:19,320 --> 00:38:20,450
is my perfect match.

713
00:38:20,920 --> 00:38:23,530
♪ Together, we fall ♪

714
00:38:26,130 --> 00:38:27,310
♪ Must it take heartache ♪

715
00:38:27,390 --> 00:38:29,300
♪ To know my heart belongs to you? ♪

716
00:38:30,200 --> 00:38:32,240
♪ Hearts cold no more ♪

717
00:38:32,380 --> 00:38:33,860
♪ Is every sweet dream ♪

718
00:38:33,900 --> 00:38:35,780
♪ Destined to fade away? ♪

719
00:38:36,910 --> 00:38:38,380
♪ Don't let it end in smoke ♪

720
00:38:38,850 --> 00:38:40,260
♪ Love and hate ♪

721
00:38:40,300 --> 00:38:41,580
♪ Till the very end ♪

722
00:38:42,490 --> 00:38:44,590
♪ Hold nothing back ♪

723
00:38:45,340 --> 00:38:47,000
♪ Never back down ♪

724
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:48,390
♪ Hold my ground ♪

725
00:38:49,580 --> 00:38:50,830
♪ Till I've given my all ♪

726
00:38:51,590 --> 00:38:55,540
♪ Come what may, we will be ♪

727
00:38:56,640 --> 00:38:59,130
♪ Forevermore ♪

728
00:39:25,790 --> 00:39:27,080
♪ How much love ♪

729
00:39:27,150 --> 00:39:29,630
♪ Is enough to be wasted? ♪

730
00:39:32,010 --> 00:39:33,550
♪ I haven't forgiven you ♪

731
00:39:33,690 --> 00:39:35,900
♪ So don't you forgive me ♪

732
00:39:38,250 --> 00:39:40,380
♪ Let the wildfire ♪

733
00:39:40,580 --> 00:39:43,340
♪ Consume us and burn us to ashes ♪

734
00:39:44,510 --> 00:39:46,500
♪ Still, we choose to be moths ♪

735
00:39:46,730 --> 00:39:49,740
♪ Flying into the flames ♪

736
00:39:51,760 --> 00:39:53,200
♪ Must it take heartache ♪

737
00:39:53,340 --> 00:39:55,190
♪ To know my heart belongs to you? ♪

738
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:57,880
♪ Hearts cold no more ♪

739
00:39:58,630 --> 00:39:59,880
♪ Is every sweet dream ♪

740
00:40:00,080 --> 00:40:01,910
♪ Destined to fade away? ♪

741
00:40:02,700 --> 00:40:04,550
♪ Don't let it end in smoke ♪

742
00:40:05,120 --> 00:40:06,700
♪ Never back down ♪

743
00:40:06,830 --> 00:40:08,110
♪ Hold my ground ♪

744
00:40:08,790 --> 00:40:10,600
♪ Till I've given my all ♪

745
00:40:11,610 --> 00:40:14,990
♪ Come what may, we will be ♪

746
00:40:16,570 --> 00:40:18,950
♪ Forevermore ♪

747
00:40:31,450 --> 00:40:32,710
♪ Let the tears fall ♪

748
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:34,100
♪ Let the blood spill ♪

749
00:40:34,980 --> 00:40:37,140
♪ Even through suffering,
I'll never let go of your hand ♪

750
00:40:38,130 --> 00:40:39,410
♪ I can't break free ♪

751
00:40:39,520 --> 00:40:40,740
♪ I can't escape ♪

752
00:40:41,350 --> 00:40:43,290
♪ This, too, can be called
a lifetime together ♪

753
00:40:43,910 --> 00:40:48,270
♪ We remain bound by fate until the end ♪

754
00:40:49,490 --> 00:40:55,350
♪ Forevermore ♪
